{
  "texts": [
    "It is worth noting that the evidence from authorities is not always expressed in the textual body of the tweet.",
    "We considered the case when some authorities may post evidence as an announcement embedded in an image or video.",
    "We present our dataset statistics in Table 4.",
    "Our data were annotated by one of the authors, a PhD candidate and native Arabic speaker working on rumor verification in Twitter.",
    "To measure the quality of our data, we randomly picked 10% of the pairs and asked a second annotator, a PhD holder and native Arabic speaker, to label them."
  ]
}